graph TD
    A[User Prompt] --> B{Agentic LLM / Core Loop}
    
    subgraph Reasoning Phase
    B -->|Thought: What should I do?| C[Decision: Call Tool or Return Final Answer]
    end
    
    subgraph Action Phase
    C -->|Tool Chosen| D[Execute @tool Python Function]
    D -->|Tool Returns Data| E[Observation Added to Context]
    end
    
    E --> B
    C -->|No Tools Needed| F[Format Final Output via Pydantic]
    F --> G[Structured JSON Response]
